name: Dorch Vangur
content: Dorch Vangur was a handsome male Human Lieutenant of the Imperial Navy for the Imperial Remnant loyal to Head of State Jagged Fel in 44 ABY, commanding the frigate Consolidator that supported the Imperial Hand Tahiri Veila during the Raid on Hagamoor 3 and ordered the orbital bombardement that cleaned the place after the mission. During the mission to Hagamoor 3, Vangur spent most of his time flirting with Tahiri, something she liked because it distracted her.
